## 🗒️ Sticky 3: Input Format (Sample)
**Expected JSON**
```json
{
  "imageUrl": "https://example.com/dish.jpg"
  // or
  // "imageBase64": "data:image/jpeg;base64,...."
}
```
**Notes**
- Template assumes **one image** per request (extend with arrays for multiple images)
- If you receive platform-specific payloads (e.g., Telegram `file_id`, LINE message objects), **normalize** them first to `imageUrl` or `imageBase64` before calling the LLM
